<?xml version="1.0"?>
<Experiment xmlns:dt="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:datatypes"><General><Version><Major dt:dt="ui4">3</Major><Minor dt:dt="ui4">0</Minor><Internal dt:dt="ui4">3</Internal><Build dt:dt="ui4">219</Build><_VersionPersist dt:dt="int">300</_VersionPersist></Version></General><ExperimentObject><Guid dt:dt="string"/><Root dt:dt="string"/><Name dt:dt="string"/><Author dt:dt="string">Psychology Software Tools, Inc.</Author><Abstract dt:dt="string">This task is designed to measure a participant's ability to accurately recall a string of digits. The participant is shown a series of digits. The minimum length of digits presented is 3 (e.g., 638) and the maximum length is 9 (e.g., 628295702). The participant has to recall the digits in the reverse order they were presented. For example, if a participant sees "389", they will need to recall "983".

Depending on whether the participant answers correctly, the task may become more difficult. If the participant gets 2 answers correct on a block, then digit length is increased. If the participant only gets 1 answer correct, then the block of trials is repeated again with different numbers even though the digit length remains the same. If a participant does not get any correct answers for a certain digit length, then the experiment concludes. 

Responses are made with the keyboard and are shown in an Echo Client during the CollectResponse TextDisplay. 


THIS CODE AND INFORMATION IS PROVIDED "AS IS" 
WITHOUT WARRANTY OF ANY KIND, EITHER EXPRESSED 
OR IMPLIED, INCLUDING BUT NOT LIMITED TO THE IMPLIED
WARRANTIES OF MERCHANTABILITY AND/OR FITNESS FOR 
A PARTICULAR PURPOSE. </Abstract><Notes dt:dt="string"></Notes><ClockGuid dt:dt="string"/><ClockIndex dt:dt="int"/><ClockScale dt:dt="r8"/><Windowed dt:dt="boolean"/><VersionMajor dt:dt="int">3</VersionMajor><VersionMinor dt:dt="int">0</VersionMinor><VersionInternal dt:dt="int">3</VersionInternal><VersionBuild dt:dt="int">80</VersionBuild><VersionAutoIncrement dt:dt="boolean">0</VersionAutoIncrement><CreationDateUtc dt:dt="dateTime">2020-03-06T16:01:22.000</CreationDateUtc><Features dt:dt="int">1073741824</Features><Devices/><Packages/><DataFile/><StartupInfo/><AdvisorModuleInstanceManager/><SlideButtonThemeManager/></ExperimentObject><StudioItems/><ToolboxDefaults xmlns:dt="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:datatypes"/><UserScript dt:dt="string"/><TestMode/><Doc dt:dt="string">IVeW5hMqBXkgjLNNVMAgfCsMWgClINHQLLQ/DVsFk0UsV+NYPmqvZ78XFKOTkVWUL/Il38w4IUFvO58+
